                        <item xml:id="e1">- Crude note introducing the Acts of the Apostles: <locus target="#69va">69va-</locus>vb.
 - Note introducing the Acts of
                           the Apostles: <locus target="#69vb">69vb</locus>.
 - Crude copy of
                           the incipit of the Second Epistle of Peter: <locus target="#103v">103v</locus>.
 - Crude copy of the incipit of the Third Epistle
                           of Peter: <locus target="#112va">112va</locus>.
 - Note: <locus target="#141v">141v</locus>.
 - Numerous corrections written over
                           erasures: e.g., <locus target="#12ra">12ra</locus>, 12va, 20ra, 20vb,
                           54vb, 105ra, 108vb, 115rb, 130rb-130va; or written interlineally in the
                           same or in a secondary (?) hand: e.g., 100vb, 101ra.
 - Commentaries
                           written in the margin: <locus target="#137v">137v</locus>, 138r.
 - A
                           portion of the text washed out: <locus target="#111rb">111rb</locus>.</item>
